Common.Strapline.Common.Text: FITTED OUT SUITES REPRESENTING GREAT VALUE - CENTRAL NORTH SYDNEY

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
51 Berry Street offers a truly unique opportunity for an occupant seeking creative office space with a focus on ‘wellness’. Construction is complete, redeveloping this boutique asset, offering 3,500sqm across 5 levels. Each floor benefits from large balconies with an expansive green outlook over Berry Street. The asset itself sits off the boundary of its neighboring buildings, therefore providing incredible natural light. 

The asset has a centre core with lifts facing the large windows on to the balconies. The efficiency of the core allows for easy space planning with the option of internal staircases between the floors. The incoming tenant has the chance to bespoke the finishes with the possibilities endless including polished concrete, exposed ceilings, feature lighting and more. 
The double height lobby gives a presence on Berry Street. The successful café on the ground floor is being kept but has been upgraded in line with the new design including railings and awning. There are market leading end of trip facilities being installed including showers, change rooms, lockers and bike racks. 

Complementing the boutique flavor of this asset is an optional rooftop terrace which has been DA approved. Accessible via a staircase or lift bank, this addition to the asset is distinctive to 51 Berry Street and is a true point of difference. The level of architectural design is proposed to be collaborated with an incoming tenant. Having space available to employees can have positive HR and productivity outcomes for your business. The rooftop gives leafy green views from 51 Berry that are definitely worth a look!

Not very often does something like this come to the market. Please contact our agents for further information.
